      "cookedHtml": "<p>Can we see all recent pulse updated by using filter option?<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/c/c01dac7f087e1b6e120b9a3e1bac4cd5b85b0392.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/c/c01dac7f087e1b6e120b9a3e1bac4cd5b85b0392_2_690x267.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"267\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">819×317 17 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>"
