    {
      "id": 82246,
      "postNumber": 2,
      "createdAt": "2022-04-07T08:45:47.897Z",
      "author": "jailynnlucidday (Jai-Lynn Hoops)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/nisha\">@Nisha</a> !</p>\n<p>So there are a few options to help you get the filter that you want.</p>\n<p>First I would create a Date column that will help capture that most recent activity date.</p>\n<p>Then you can create the criteria for when that date column updates by using custom automations.</p>\n<p>Here are two of my favorite:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/2/23e0375d1a0275e9815ffea45ea508b697439868.png\" title=\"When Status Changes\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/2/23e0375d1a0275e9815ffea45ea508b697439868_2_689x445.png\" alt=\"When Status Changes\" width=\"689\" height=\"445\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">When Status Changes</span><span class=\"informations\">1106×714 26.7 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/3/3a083cb525f16da7b4f8933a9b0cef73e625b940.png\" title=\"When Update is Created\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/3/3a083cb525f16da7b4f8933a9b0cef73e625b940_2_667x500.png\" alt=\"When Update is Created\" width=\"667\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">When Update is Created</span><span class=\"informations\">852×638 21.9 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>You will then be able to use the Date filter to filter out the ones that were updated today, this week, or even this month!<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/b/b665f8d50b0ffe6f12ca9d81b775ba68c050643b.png\" title=\"Date Filter\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/b/b665f8d50b0ffe6f12ca9d81b775ba68c050643b_2_690x336.png\" alt=\"Date Filter\" width=\"690\" height=\"336\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">Date Filter</span><span class=\"informations\">1482×722 70.3 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>(If you wanna get fancy, you can even use conditional coloring with the same rules to highlight the most recent updates).</p>\n<p>Hope this helps!</p>"
    },
